verses.text_plain: The Lord reigneth; let the people tremble: he sitteth between the cherubims; let the earth be moved.
verses.verse_html:
1The Lord reigneth; let the people tremble: he sitteth between the cherubims; let the earth be moved. ▼
▼ be moved: Heb. stagger

footnotes.body_html: ▼ be moved: Heb. stagger

verses.text_plain: The Lord is great in Zion; and he is high above all the people.
verses.verse_html: 2The Lord is great in Zion; and he is high above all the people.

verses.text_plain: Let them praise thy great and terrible name; for it is holy.
verses.verse_html: 3Let them praise thy great and terrible name; for it is holy.

verses.text_plain: The king’s strength also loveth judgment; thou dost establish equity, thou executest judgment and righteousness in Jacob.
verses.verse_html: 4The king’s strength also loveth judgment; thou dost establish equity, thou executest judgment and righteousness in Jacob.

verses.text_plain: Exalt ye the Lord our God, and worship at his footstool; for he is holy.
verses.verse_html:
5Exalt ye the Lord our God, and worship at his footstool; for he is holy. ▼
▼ he is…: or, it is holy

footnotes.body_text: ▼ he is…: or, it is holy
footnotes.body_html: ▼ he is…: or, it is holy

verses.text_plain: Moses and Aaron among his priests, and Samuel among them that call upon his name; they called upon the Lord, and he answered them.
verses.verse_html: 6Moses and Aaron among his priests, and Samuel among them that call upon his name; they called upon the Lord, and he answered them.

verses.text_plain: He spake unto them in the cloudy pillar: they kept his testimonies, and the ordinance that he gave them.
verses.verse_html: 7He spake unto them in the cloudy pillar: they kept his testimonies, and the ordinance that he gave them.

verses.text_plain: Thou answeredst them, O Lord our God: thou wast a God that forgavest them, though thou tookest vengeance of their inventions.
verses.verse_html: 8Thou answeredst them, O Lord our God: thou wast a God that forgavest them, though thou tookest vengeance of their inventions.

verses.text_plain: Exalt the Lord our God, and worship at his holy hill; for the Lord our God is holy.
verses.verse_html: 9Exalt the Lord our God, and worship at his holy hill; for the Lord our God is holy.
